  "title": "Operation Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Schedule job, set priorities, monitor job progress and tracking schedules, communicate changes on job status.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for daily drivers’ and equipment planning and deployment</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and interface with internal and external customers to ensure on time deliveries and collections</li>\n  <li>Liaise with all departments / customers for all job execution</li>\n  <li>Handle customers’ complaints, drivers’ feedback and problems.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that all records in the Control Department are updated accurately.</li>\n  <li>Any other tasks as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ability to respond to ad-hoc and urgent demand on timely and professionally</li>\n  <li>Ability to multitask and work under a fast pace environment</li>\n  <li>Computer literate, independent with good interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills and must be Bilingual.</li>\n</ul>",
